        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 6. Plumulojassa ocia (Bate, 1862). Le Croisic, France, date unknown, E. Chevreux, coll., MNHNAm. 2664. Tip of right uropod 1 inner and outer rami, showing the fringe of cusps on the apex of the outer ramus. X5000." ;
